beneficiaries of Funds to receive their payments being delayed or
denied by various authorities and countries.
Your expected Revenue according to available information in our file
is $10.5M (Ten Million, Five Hundred Thousand United States Dollars)
only, representing the amount unpaid to you from your
Compensation/Inheritance funds
 As a matter of urgency, 
please provide us all the listed information
below to enable us proceed with the transfer of your
Compensation/Inheritance funds into your bank account without any
delay..
(1) Your Full Names   ;..................
(2) Your Contact Address : ...............
(3) Your Contact Phone numbers :...........

However, be informed that this INFORMATION is real and not contrary to

Thanks
Mr. Terry Tuggle
FIRST NATIONAL BANK TEXAS

subject: Re: FIRST NATIONAL BANK TEXAS.
body:
Hello Mr. Terry Tuggle,

Thank you for reaching out to me from the FIRST NATIONAL BANK TEXAS. It's quite surprising to hear about this agreement reached by President Joe Biden and other world Presidents. I must say, it's a significant step towards resolving delayed or denied payments.

The amount mentioned, Ten Million, Five Hundred Thousand United States Dollars, is indeed a substantial sum. However, I'm curious as to why my funds were unpaid in the first place? Could you provide more details on that?

Also, could you please elaborate on the role of the committee set up by the US government? How do they monitor these payments?

I appreciate your assistance and look forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Kayla
